reviews.title: Awesome App!
reviews.comment: I\'ve been training for 7 weeks now and love it, but now it\'s getting intense so I\'m kinda losing my motivation. I did have an issue where the app would close just before I was done the work out, I don\'t know why tho.
reviews.author: missmustanggurl

reviews.title: Barely works
reviews.comment: Last 2 weeks, I have tried using this app.. it shuts off on me. I have it set up to hear a beep and hear the voice, well I never hear either. Im using the \'music play list\' through the app so it\'s not like 1 program over does another. Im deleting and looking for a new app..
reviews.author: Stephanie Ramsey

reviews.title: Keeps shutting down in the middle of a run
reviews.comment: The app keeps shutting down / force close in the middle of a run. Then I have to stop running, restart app, forward to approx time the app stopped ... Too much hassle. Uninstalled.
reviews.author: Poh Yoke Lo

reviews.title: Good app
reviews.comment: App is easy and convenient to use. My only complaint about it is that it shuts down when you receive a phone call or text message and doesn\'t save where you are in the run. So you have to stop running, restart the program, and fast forward through the workout until you get back to the place you were. I have discovered though if I put my phone on airplane mode it won\'t do this, but then you can\'t use any gps programs to map the run. I would give it 5 stars if the program stayed running in the background.
reviews.author: Julie Sage

reviews.title: \"Who does Taylor Swift think she is anyway?\"
reviews.comment: Am I hearing things, or is the \'Trainer\' making comments about Taylor Swift?  LOL! Can you make the trainer make comments about Miley Cyrus too? Wait... That would mean I\'d have to listen to her horrible music! Love the humor you guys inject - keep it up!!!! :-)

reviews.title: I\'m up to 5K!
reviews.comment: It\'s great to have a free trainer that does the basics, just telling me when to start and stop running. The only problem I have with this program is that some of the days don\'t complete themselves, so I don\'t have a record on my phone of when or whether I finished that day\'s assignment.
